  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec.md §6">Side-pane structure per spec §6: Search Index dropdown at top (replaces 4 tabs); existing filters keep label-above-control layout; Relevance Threshold + Search Mode moved IN below filters; Search button at bottom.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec.md §6.5">Use Choice's `@OData.Community.Display.V1.FormattedValue` (label string), NOT the integer value, for entity-type derivation. Normalize via `toLowerCase + replace(/\s+/g, '')`. "All" label → `scope: 'all'` (no entityType filter).</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-021">Fluent UI v9 + `tokens.*` for all styling. No hex literals. Dark-mode tokens for the new Dropdown + Popover.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-022">React 18 in code pages (different boundary from PCF which is React 16).</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-028">Dataverse Web API call uses `credentials: 'include'` for the user session cookie; not via `authenticatedFetch` (which is for BFF). Dataverse OAuth is the user's session in the code page.</constraint>
    <constraint source="NFR-11">Code page clean-rebuild required before deploy (rm -rf out/; npm run build) — covered in task 109.</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
